{"tid":1390767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（熟讀）警察宣誓哲詞","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:57.000Z","uid":261986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0fbd3e83a244cd2ea68db5fe183d405c35eef2","tid":1390767,"uid":261986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依法</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為香港特別行政區政府效力</span></span>為警務人員，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度</span></span>行使職權，執行職務，並且<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令</span></span>[1]。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以像霸氣哥咁提下警察叔叔，可能佢地記得Ｄ唔記得Ｄ。"},{"pid":"826634770a9184e0fbad55cc5fb6cef5569a3784","tid":1390767,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"}]}